'''Dhumbudya''': aya [[zvipembenene]] zvinodyiwa uye zvakafanana ne[[mhashu]] asi zvakatitsongei zviri zwidiki uyewo zviine muviri uneruvara rwepfumbi rwakafanana nemashizha emiti. Zvinonyanya kuonekwa munguva yokunaya kwemvura. Madhumbudya anobhururukawo semhashu. Madhumbudya, kana abikwa, ane mafuta akawanda kudarika mhashu.
